self.setUpClass()
num_qubits = 1
p = ql.Program('test_unitary_IYZ', platform, num_qubits)
k = ql.Kernel('akernel', platform, num_qubits)
u = ql.Unitary('X', [complex(0.0, 0.0), complex(1.0, 0.0), complex(1.0, 0.0
    ), complex(0.0, 0.0)])
u1 = ql.Unitary('y', [complex(0.0, 0.0), complex(0.0, -1.0), complex(0.0, 
    1.0), complex(0.0, 0.0)])
u2 = ql.Unitary('Z', [complex(1.0, 0.0), complex(0.0, 0.0), complex(0.0, 
    0.0), complex(-1.0, 0.0)])
u.decompose()
u1.decompose()
u2.decompose()
k.gate('hadamard', [0])
k.gate(u, [0])
k.gate(u1, [0])
k.gate(u2, [0])
p.add_kernel(k)
p.compile()
qx.set(os.path.join(output_dir, p.name + '_initialqasmwriter_out.qasm'))
qx.execute()
c0 = qx.get_state()
self.assertAlmostEqual(0.5, helper_regex(c0)[0], 5)
self.assertAlmostEqual(0.5, helper_regex(c0)[1], 5)
